Query 1 – Find all vegan appetizers:
SELECT RecipeName, PrepTime FROM Recipes WHERE CourseType = 'appetizer' AND DietaryTag = 'vegan';

Query 2 – Check inventory for ingredients below reorder level:
SELECT IngredientName, CurrentStock, ReorderLevel FROM Ingredients WHERE CurrentStock < ReorderLevel ORDER BY CurrentStock ASC;

Query 3 – List all recipes using expensive ingredients (cost > $5):
SELECT DISTINCT Recipes.RecipeName FROM Recipes JOIN RecipeIngredients ON Recipes.RecipeID = RecipeIngredients.RecipeID JOIN Ingredients ON RecipeIngredients.IngredientID = Ingredients.IngredientID WHERE Ingredients.CostPerUnit > 5.00;

Query 4 – Get supplier contact info for recipes we're making today:
SELECT DISTINCT Suppliers.CompanyName, Suppliers.ContactEmail FROM Suppliers JOIN Ingredients ON Suppliers.SupplierID = Ingredients.SupplierID JOIN RecipeIngredients ON Ingredients.IngredientID = RecipeIngredients.IngredientID WHERE RecipeIngredients.RecipeID IN (SELECT RecipeID FROM TodaysMenu);

Each query answers a real operational question Chef Laurent faces daily.
